<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <%- include('layout/head') %>
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.1.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body id="body" class="index">

  <header id="header">
    <%- include('layout/header') %>
  </header>

  <main id="main">
    <p id="instructions">
      The mantra "no regrets" stems from a lack of information.
      <br />
      HindSite Trader is a tool to cleanse you of your blissful ignorance and quantify your regrets.
      <br />
      <br />
      Do you <em>really</em> want your "what-if"s answered?
      <br />
      Fill in the blanks to get a <strong>real</strong> answer to a question we've all asked ourselves.
    </p>

    <form action="/result" method="post" id="search-form">
      <fieldset class="fieldset">
        <label>If I invested: <input name="search" type="number" min="0.01" step="0.01" max="100,000"
            placeholder="$1000.00" required /></label>
        <label>in:<input name="search" type="text" placeholder="a public company" required /></label>
        <label>on: <input name="search" type="month" min="1998-01" max="2019-03" value="1998-01" class="dateclass" required /> <em>(Sometime in the past 20 years)</em></label>
      </fieldset>

      <label class="submit-button-label">
        How much richer would I be?<button type="submit">Find Out!</button>
      </label>
    </form>

  </main>

  <footer id="footer">
    <%- include('layout/footer') %>
  </footer>

</body>

</html>